  "texts": [
    "CLEAR's use of NER aligns with a robust precedent in RAG methodologies.",
    "A recent review of RAG approaches included 16 studies that incorporate entity recognition and entity-based reasoning in different ways for RAG 53.",
    "For instance, NER can be employed to edit or revise generated content.",
    "In CBRKBQA, NER aids in revising results by aligning generated relations with those in the local neighborhood of the query entity within a knowledge graph 54.",
    "Similarly, GMT-KBQA re-ranks retrieved entities and relations and conducts relation classification and entity disambiguation prior to generation 55."
  ],
